name: AVSampleCursorDependencyInfo
desc: A value for describing dependencies between a media sample and other media samples in the same sample sequence.

items.name: var sampleIndicatesWhetherItHasDependentSamples: ObjCBool
items.desc: A Boolean value that determines whether the sample indicates if other samples depend on it.

items.name: var sampleHasDependentSamples: ObjCBool
items.desc: A Boolean value that determines whether the sample has dependent samples.

items.name: var sampleIndicatesWhetherItDependsOnOthers: ObjCBool
items.desc: A Boolean value that determines whether the sample indicates that it depends on other samples.

items.name: var sampleDependsOnOthers: ObjCBool
items.desc: A Boolean value that determines whether the sample depends on other samples.

items.name: var sampleIndicatesWhetherItHasRedundantCoding: ObjCBool
items.desc: A Boolean value that determines whether the sample indicates that it has redundant coding.

items.name: var sampleHasRedundantCoding: ObjCBool
items.desc: A Boolean value that determines whether the sample has redundant coding.

items.name: init()
items.desc: Creates a sample cursor dependency information structure.

items.name: init(sampleIndicatesWhetherItHasDependentSamples: ObjCBool, sampleHasDependentSamples: ObjCBool, sampleIndicatesWhetherItDependsOnOthers: ObjCBool, sampleDependsOnOthers: ObjCBool, sampleIndicatesWhetherItHasRedundantCoding: ObjCBool, sampleHasRedundantCoding: ObjCBool)
items.desc: Creates a sample cursor dependency information structure with sample information.
